* ====================================== * SUB: Custom column data * Reads any custom column data from a global variable * ====================================== sub.DoCustom: $custom.data = get global variable: name='egosoft.browser.custom' if $custom.data $custom.key = get next key: table=$custom.data key=null while $custom.key $custom.array = $custom.data[$custom.key] $text = $custom.data[$custom.key][0] $table.column.names[$custom.key] = $text $text = $custom.data[$custom.key][1] $table.column.longnames[$custom.key] = $text $text = $custom.data[$custom.key][2] $table.columns[$custom.key] = $text $data = $custom.data[$custom.key][3] do if $data $table.sort.extras[$custom.key] = $data do if $custom.data[$custom.key][4] $table.columns.dontsort[$custom.key] = [TRUE]
$custom.key = get next key: table=$custom.data key=$custom.key end end return null
